'''Al-Farisi''' (lit. "the Persian") may refer to:

* [[Kamāl al-Dīn al-Fārisī]] (d. 1319) optician and mathematician.
* [[Muhammad ibn Abi Bakr al‐Farisi]] (d. 1278-9) astronomer born in Aden and author of ''al-Tuḥfa''.

